1.患者男性，63岁，既往高血压病史5年，最高峰值：160/106mmHg,曾服用&ldquo;硝苯地平缓释片、吲达帕胺片及厄贝沙坦片&rdquo;以降压治疗。否认糖尿病病史。2.主要特点：头晕，伴有视物旋转，时有头痛，巅顶为主，痛处固定，劳累及情绪激动加重，甚则如坐舟船，平卧后好转，时有耳鸣，时有鼻塞、流涕，无异味，受风后流涕加重，大便干燥，饮食欠佳，睡眠不实，无发热及畏寒，无肢体及语言活动障碍，无恶心及呕吐，无腹泻等症状。3.查体：T&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt;'&gt; 36.2℃，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt;'&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;P80&lt;/span&gt;分&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;、R18&lt;/span&gt;次∕分&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;、BP140/80mmHg，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt;'&gt;咽部无充血，两侧扁桃体无肿大，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 楷体_GB2312;'&gt;口唇无紫绀，颈软无压痛，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style='font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 14.0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 楷体_GB2312; mso-bidi-font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-font-kerning: 1.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: 楷体_GB2312;'&gt;两肺呼吸动度一致，语颤一致，听诊两肺呼吸音清，两肺听诊未闻及干湿性啰音。四肢肌力、肌张力正常，神经系统检查无阳性体征，余未见异常。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-US&quot; style='font-family: 楷体_GB2312; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-fon